- "Active targets" refer to energy consumption targets that are currently in effect;
- "Relevant time periods" are the start and end dates defined for each target;
- "Average target energy consumption" is the mean of all target energy consumption values for a location;
- "Average actual energy consumption" is the mean of all actual energy consumption values for a location during the target periods.

